    <main>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
          <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1 order-2 box1 align-content-center">
            <div
              class="components d-flex justify-content-center design flex-column"
            >
              <div class="rect r1"></div>
              <div class="rect r2"></div>
              <div class="rect r3"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2 order-1 align-self-center p-1">
            <div class="heading text-center text-md-left">
              <h1 class="oswald-heading">TopAnimeApi</h1>
              <p class="p mt-4 roboto-regular">
                TopAnimeApi is an open-source REST API for the
                <em
                  ><strong
                    >List of top ranking anime and their details</strong
                  ></em
                >. TopAnimeAPI is your one-stop destination for accessing
                comprehensive rankings and detailed information on the top anime
                series. <br />
                Whether you're an avid anime fan, a developer working on a
                personal project,TopAnimeAPI offers the tools and resources you
                need to explore, discover, and utilize anime data in innovative
                ways.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-start mt-3 p-1">
              <a
                href="https://github.com/nirajan128/topAnimeAPI"
                target="_blank"
                ><button class="btn primary">Learn More</button></a
              >
              <a href="#get-started"
                ><button class="btn secondary ml-2">Get Started</button></a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="conatiner2 p-3 mt-5 mr-5 ml-5" id="get-started">
        <div class="info">
          <div class="info-heading">
            <h2 class="oswald-heading">Documentations</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="info-content roboto-regular">
            <p>
              A free,fast, and clean REST API which thats easy to use.The API
              returns the data in <b>JSON format</b>
            </p>
            <p>
              Base URL:
              <a href="https://topanimeapi.onrender.com/"
                >https://topanimeapi.onrender.com/</a
              >
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="table-content table-responsive">
          <table
            class="table table-light table-striped table-hover table-extra the-table overflow-hidden"
          >
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th scope="col">Method</th>
                <th scope="col">URL</th>
                <th scope="col">Returns</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row">GET</th>
                <td>baseURL/anime</td>
                <td>All anime details in the database</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row">GET</th>
                <td>baseURL/anime/random</td>
                <td>Random anime each time</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row">GET</th>
                <td>baseURL/anime/search?q='animename'</td>
                <td>
                  searched anime which is eneterd in query parameter <br />
                  example: baserURL/anime/search/?q=gintama returns all anime
                  with name gintama
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
